{"tid":1865732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍灣潘任惠珍議員真係寸過馬撚","createTime":"2020-02-06T10:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T16:13:41.000Z","uid":259650,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9b783d08ad08b696ee9961e63dc8f5412b64ad","tid":1865732,"uid":259650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:45:35.000Z","msg":"呢個自稱民主派嘅廢老食哂人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身德福班街坊都覺得佢廢柴<br />\n諗住無為而治都算 好過益左保皇<br />\n點知佢何止無為 仲寸過馬撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊睇下佢個page點應街坊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n街坊話佢廢柴唔做野衰過另一個同區議員<br />\n佢竟然可以咁厚面皮答<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">能者多勞 天經地義</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxywh6g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxywh6g.jpg&h=f5cad586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲意思話塞緊錢入新議員袋培養緊人地咁話喎 <br />\n真係多謝晒你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後繼續寸寸貢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DwDTwtC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDwDTwtC.jpg&h=2fe65df1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔講真係以為同緊何妖講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5yL62A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5yL62A.jpg&h=6c210dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實呢個廢老之前已經有好多豐功偉績<br />\n例如之前德福同popo打仗<br />\n街坊搵佢求救發現佢一選舉完就走左去渡假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pghYaB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pghYaB.jpg&h=39b67ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n永遠搵唔到呢位議員<br />\n有人提出質疑仲咬返人地轉頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOdkbw2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOdkbw2.jpg&h=a8a1245b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要自立版規咁話 黑警到學返黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BY3kbwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBY3kbwH.jpg&h=d09cec9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢位尊敬嘅潘任惠珍議員聽講已經任職35年<br />\n上年好多新選民見佢係獨立/自稱民主就繼續投左佢<br />\n請各位認清楚呢啲老鼠屎 <br />\n人地唔稀罕逗份人工 唔稀罕做區議員<br />\n求求有能之人考慮下他日取替呢啲廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎大家多啲去fb同潘太吹下水 記得守版規呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7da64dd467ddea4612ad858759c3d134d4f6ea","tid":1865732,"uid":259650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:49:10.000Z","msg":"p仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3630cddc98a50d803aeecf137177b4cc45f22cf","tid":1865732,"uid":259650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:01:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1c05bffa75afce739eeb4bbd95be36d0a2821b0","tid":1865732,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:02:01.000Z","msg":"清算師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2248a76a9622367a5ee55a9ecb8fcf6219c8eb93","tid":1865732,"uid":45753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:03:10.000Z","msg":"益乜9保皇 另一個對手唔係大學生咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係既自己抵死"},{"pid":"ae4135b0053657f9d71a8ebe91f32d9f48227982","tid":1865732,"uid":259650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2248a76a9622367a5ee55a9ecb8fcf6219c8eb93","tid":1865732,"uid":45753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:03:10.000Z","msg":"益乜9保皇 另一個對手唔係大學生咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係既自己抵死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:12:32.000Z","msg":"之前喺德福街坊gp見好多新選民話以為佢民主派就投左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能另一位又唔夠時間宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申冇得投嗰區"},{"pid":"e83144dc51405afd543830527643bd111c1719ae","tid":1865732,"uid":259650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"清算師mark低佢呀唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推唔郁都推"}]}